keepsNodes.title: archetype:generate
keepsNodes.description: Generates a new project from an existing Maven archetype.

keepsNodes.title: clean
keepsNodes.description: Cleans the build artifacts, removing the target directory.

keepsNodes.title: clean install
keepsNodes.description: Clean the project, compile, package, and install the artifact to the local repository.

keepsNodes.title: clean install skip tests
keepsNodes.description:
Clean the project, compile, package, and install the artifact to the local repository.
But, do not run tests.

keepsNodes.title: clean package
keepsNodes.description: Cleans the project, compiles it, and packages the compiled code into an executable format.

keepsNodes.title: clean test
keepsNodes.description: Cleans the project, compiles it, and runs the unit tests.

keepsNodes.title: compile
keepsNodes.description: Compiles the source code of the project.

keepsNodes.title: dependency:tree
keepsNodes.description: Displays the dependency tree of the project, showing all the dependencies and their versions.

keepsNodes.title: deploy
keepsNodes.description: Deploys the packaged artifact to a remote Maven repository.

keepsNodes.title: install
keepsNodes.description: Installs the packaged artifact into the local Maven repository, making it available for other projects to use as a dependency.

keepsNodes.title: package
keepsNodes.description: Packages the compiled code into an executable JAR, WAR, or other distribution format.

keepsNodes.title: test
keepsNodes.description: Runs the unit tests of the project.

keepsNodes.title: verify
keepsNodes.description: Runs integration tests and additional checks to verify the quality of the project.
